project.name: Group Project: Our Economic Lives
description: The goal of this project is to help individuals either advance further in their chosen career path, or get started working towards a new path. The central element of the app is their industry pyramid which is made up of various tiers. Each tier is composed of building block that will have a description, some examples, and a place for them to enter personal examples of how they possess that trait.

My primary role in this project was making the pyramid and linking it to the data in the database. When a user selects a tier, the user is then presented with a set of links for each building block in that tier. When they select a building block it will take them to blocks page and display any info they have already input.
Technologies used Material-Ui, React, JavaScript, HTML, Redux, Express, Node.js, PostgreSQL
